## Create question


### Resource

`<%= ENV['DOMAIN_NAME'] %>/v1/interventions/:intervention_id/questions`


### URL parameters

Parameter | Description | Required
--------- | ----------- | --------
intervention_id | Intervention ID | yes


### Query String

Parameter | Description | Required
--------- | ----------- | --------


### HTTP request method

`POST`


### HTTP headers

<%= partial 'includes/http/headers/auth' %>


### HTTP body

{
	"question": {
		"type": "Question::Name",
		"title": "question example title",
		"subtitle": "question example subtitle",
		"body": [
		  {
		    "payload": "yes",
		    "var": "1"
		  }
		]
	}
}



### Note
Required keys:
* `title`;
* `type`.

`type` key has to contains one of the following values:
* `Question::AnalogueScale`;
* `Question::BarGraph`;
* `Question::Feedback`;
* `Question::FollowUpContact`;
* `Question::Grid`;
* `Question::Information`;
* `Question::Multiple`;
* `Question::Number`;
* `Question::Single`;
* `Question::TextBox`;
* `Question::Url`.


> HTTP example request

```http
POST <%= ENV['DOMAIN_NAME'] %>/v1/interventions/1/questions
```

```http
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
access-token: xxxyyyzzz
token-type: Bearer
client: xxxyyyzzz
uid: user@<%= ENV['DOMAIN_NAME'] %>
```

```json
{
	"question": {
		"type": "Question::Name",
		"title": "question example title",
		"subtitle": "question example subtitle",
		"body": [
		  {
		    "payload": "yes",
		    "var": "1"
		  }
		]
	}
}
```


> HTTP response 200 OK







